{"tid":33652,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益] 成語動畫廊之請食檸檬","createTime":"2016-12-11T03:01:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T03:05:08.000Z","uid":55952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7db2fa482d76797e2b7a58c20306a60a1f903ffc","tid":33652,"uid":55952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T03:01:50.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n我喺英國住緊hall 有個兄弟最近教緊個蝗三代中文 三個半鐘前醉醉地衝入嚟話好撚sad 話琴晚畀人請食檸檬 我頂唔順借沖涼遁走左出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 兄弟   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢女神<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：我聽日去教個蝗三代百厭蚤豆窿中文<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：其實教中文有咩好教<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：好多架 我聽日諗住去教佢啲簡單嘅成語<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：成語咁難 佢明唔明架？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有啲都好簡單 唔信我問下妳 妳試下答我啦 你知唔知痴人說夢點解？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：姐係唔會發生咁解？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：大概係咁啦 咁妳諗唔諗到啲例子？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：emmmm 你會係我男朋友算唔算係？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;咁愚公移山呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：有個白痴仔好有恆心咁劈山開路？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：係吖&hellip;&hellip;所以都凡事都講恆心同毅力嘅<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：但係呢啲都係痴人說夢 邊有可能一個人搬走座山<br />\n<br />\n就係咁 我同佢講女死女還在 佢話呢條女係真愛 而且佢都未死 邊得嚟女死女還在<br />\n<br />\n點安慰條撚樣好 呢邊已經凌晨三點 好撚眼瞓<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999<br />\n<br />\n利申 非hehe"},{"pid":"3470be0d0a8a67518eae7e987d1dcda3a2f54ddc","tid":33652,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11